CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

December 17, 2013

[Cite as 12/17/2013 Case Announcements, 2013-Ohio-5501.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2005-0569. In re Application of Olterman.

This cause came on for further consideration upon the filing of a motion to seal the record by applicant, William Olterman, on October 29, 2013. On consideration thereof, it is ordered by this court that the motion is denied.

Lanzinger and O’Neill, JJ., dissent.
